cuems-dmxplayer (0.0.0-6) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Unify release code onto main: fold in rc_1 (mtcreceiver 24h-continuity-rc2,
    OLA reconnection, adaptive timer, cold-boot MIDI/olad readiness fixes) plus
    the no-rogue-olad fix (olad auto_start=false).
  * Consolidate debian packaging onto main. Installed binary is
    /usr/bin/cuems-dmxplayer, fixing the mis-named /usr/bin/dmxplayer-cuems that
    the ad-hoc 0.0.0-5 build shipped and that broke the engine DMX-player spawn.

